cc:Work.dc:title: Gauge Example
cc:Work.dc:description: Simple gauge design to give an example of this type of design in Inkscape.

flowRoot.flowPara: Simple gauge design. See layers for each part and export indiviual layers (export to png) to build up web or desktop app gauge images separately. Also, you can spin the pointer by selecting it and putting it in rotate mode - It's axis is centered... Enjoy, Mohawke
